alerts.text:
KCON Sydney 2017 - Qudos Bank Arena, Olympic Park
8pm - 10:30pm
- Lidcombe to Olympic Park shuttle trains run every 10 minutes until 12:30am.
- Route 525 buses run between Parramatta and Burwood via Sydney Olympic Park.
- Route 526 buses run from the Sydney Olympic Park Ferry Wharf to Olympic Park.
- Route X25 buses run regularly to Sydney Olympic Park from Strathfield Station during the afternoon peak period on weekdays.
- The F3 Parramatta River Ferry service stop is approximately 40 minutes walk (3.6km) from Qudos Bank Arena. There is also connecting 526 bus to the precinct.
